      "helpText": "There are three types of messages as follows:   M for Single message (contains only one MSH segment) B for Batch of messages (contains multiple MSH segments) F for File of batches (contains multiple BHS segments)   This field is automatically filled in by the Messaging System and is used to determine the appropriate header segment to build for a message. ",
